{"tid":1334771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"720全名應該係法輪大法守護香港大集會","createTime":"2019-07-20T08:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T08:48:49.000Z","uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a8aa52acbfa0e1158baf916b0551ff53c637115b","tid":1334771,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:41:57.000Z","msg":"今天是遭受中共殘酷迫害的法輪功學員，反迫害20週年。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全球各地都舉辦了相關活動</strong></span>，美國總統川普在週三接見了法輪功學員。在台灣，法輪功學員們則舉辦了遊行和燭光悼念晚會。<br />\n<br />\n接見宗教受迫害者 川普詢問法輪功學員情況：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2LwjWL1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LwjWL1&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvblSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=2d949ba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2LwjWL1</a><br />\n<br />\n前中共黨魁江澤民自1999年7月20日起對法輪功進行滅絕性的迫害，至今長達20年。<br />\n<br />\n台灣法輪功學員每年舉辦7&middot;20遊行和悼念會，以和平理性的方式講述法輪功真相，以期喚醒人們心中的善念，共同制止中共跨世紀的反人類罪行。<br />\n<br />\n法輪功720反迫害20週年遊行暨燭光悼念會<br />\n新唐人亞太電視台直播<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ntdtv.com.tw/videos/762006830897769/UzpfSTQxMDM4MjE3MjQzMTc3MjoxNTEzMjQ0OTcyMTQ1NDgx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fntdtv.com.tw%2Fvideos%2F762006830897769%2FUzpfSTQxMDM4MjE3MjQzMTc3MjoxNTEzMjQ0OTcyMTQ1NDgx%2F&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvblSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=3a40d5f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ntdtv.com.tw/videos/762006830897769/UzpfSTQxMDM4MjE3MjQzMTc3MjoxNTEzMjQ0OTcyMTQ1NDgx/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日係法輪功反中共迫害20週年的日子，估唔倒我地香港都有支持的活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a95efecb17d910d5231175c137913e09a6c4d229","tid":1334771,"uid":283166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"推"}]}